fields.content:
### About

State of the Map(SotM) is the largest annual gathering for the mapper and user community. SotM is organized by the OSM community for the community. We thank all attendees and staff for observing it.  

SotM has an amazing variety of speakers, subjects and [keynote speakers](/2012/keynotes/)
